Spring Template : SSO
=====================

o Introduction
o Running the template
o More info

Introduction
------------
This is a Spring template to show how to use a Servlet Filter
to protect a page and inject attributes into the request once
the SSO process is complete.

Running the template
--------------------
You can see the template in action by running Jetty:
mvn jetty:run
and pointing your browser to:
http://localhost:8080/spring-template/protected

More info
---------
http://codebrane.bom/blog
